Outdoor dining doesn’t get any better than this! We had a wonderful lunch at Gondola Village at @oceanhouseri and it was the most incredible dining experience ever. We dined in one of three authentic ski gondolas and felt like we were transported to the French Alps! You know what this called for… a Shirley Temple! 🍒

Just a few more sleeps to go!
We have had so much fun this holiday season and hope you have to. This past weekend was one to remember.  Dad always talks about his hometown and now we know why! The food, views and especially the Shirley Temples were top notch. Can’t wait to be back! 

Shoutout to @oceanhouseri and @weekapauginn for the awesome memories. 

Santa - We are ready for you! 🎅🎄

What a year it has been!  Saying goodbye to an awesome 2022 and welcoming 2023 with a big smile.  Wishing you all a happy, healthy new year full of laughs, love, proud moments and incredible memories to be made! 
Thank you for all of your suppport and encouragement this past year. Your kind words mean so much! Looking forward to sharing an exciting and fun year ahead. 

Cheers to 2023! 🎉🎊🍒

As April break comes to an end we are so thankful for the amazing weather, delicious food and fun times we had in NYC! Our stay at @thepeninsulanyc was wonderful and we had the best time taking part in their Peter Rabbit New York Adventure. From the chocolates, stuffed animals and books that greeted us in our room to the plush Peter Rabbit and Pen Bear bathrobes and slippers (and so much more) we felt like royalty. Can’t wait to come back!

It’s been a minute! I’ve been so busy this past month finishing up 4th grade and FILMING A NEW MOVIE! I can’t wait to share more with you all soon.
